      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 06:04:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新兴市场货币交易员关注美国大选，推动市场波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/em-currency-traders-zero-in-on-us-election-driving-volatility</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从六年来最持续的货币波动性上升来看，美国总统大选开始让新兴市场投资者感到不安。]]></description>
